---
title: Spicy Korean Mushrooms and Lentils  with pickled radish, roasted kale and gochujang aioli drizzle
description: This is a meal that has a little bit of something for everyone. Spicy lentils cooled with coconut milk. pickled radish, crispy kale and fragrant jasmine rice are all standout elements in this delicious Korean-inspired dish.
